    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small ladles intended primarily for serving sauces; generally smaller than gravy ladles and sometimes made as part of a flatware service.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
